    <p>I am a Registered Mental Health Nurse and NHS digital health leader with over 22 years of experience spanning clinical, operational, and strategic roles at local, regional, and national level. I have held a Chief Nursing Information Officer (CNIO) position at Dorset HealthCare NHS Foundation Trust, where I led clinical safety governance for AI and digital health technologies — authoring clinical safety cases under DCB0129 and DCB0160 across eighteen deployed systems.</p>
